#!/usr/bin/env python

import rospy
import yaml
import json
import actionlib

from robotiq_c_model_control.msg import *

def execute(input_parameters, output_parameters):
	
	pub = rospy.Publisher('/CModelRobotOutput', CModel_robot_output, queue_size=100)
	
	command = CModel_robot_output()
	command2 = CModel_robot_output()
	
	rospy.sleep(1)
	
	command.rACT = 0
	command.rGTO = 0
	command.rATR = 0
	command.rPR = 0
	command.rSP = 0
	command.rFR = 0
	
	command2.rACT = 1
	command2.rGTO = 1
	command2.rATR = 0
	command2.rPR = 0
	command2.rSP = 255
	command2.rFR = 150
	
	pub.publish(command)
	rospy.sleep(1)

	pub.publish(command2)
	rospy.sleep(2)

	return output_parameters
